{"tid":1719720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[必看]屯門分部戰線十一月中期檢討(內含改善建議)","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T18:28:53.000Z","uid":134141,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0f1a5dee3d0d7e2cc14dae4e2f73ffe3c71cb0","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇哂成篇文是一種美德<br />\n睇哂成篇文都係一種抗爭</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今整個星期無論清晨深夜都有行動<br />\n見到屯門係戰略上有好大既改善空間<br />\n<br />\n第一點(最重要)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屯門牛由今日開始要將開花既重點<br />\n由八點圍魏救趙行動<br />\n轉移向6點清晨既塞鐵塞公路行動<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家夜晚唔做野<br />\n或者可以試下將夜晚既行動提早<br />\n然後塞到咁上下早少少翻屋企休息<br />\n保證自己12點前可以上床訓教<br />\n否則每次大家好有機會起唔身<br />\n而每日訓3-4個鐘<br />\n對抗爭者既身體亦都好大負荷<br />\n此舉並不利於我地長期抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">亦有好多手足起唔到身</span><br />\n<br />\n而今日4點鐘吹雞開花<br />\n係一個好好既先例<br />\n我希望大家可以開完花早d翻屋企休息<br />\n<br />\n明日旭日行動唔可以少人過今晚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明日旭日行動唔可以少人過今晚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明日旭日行動唔可以少人過今晚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以輕視塞鐵塞公路既重要性！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以輕視塞鐵塞公路既重要性！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以輕視塞鐵塞公路既重要性！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二點<br />\n請唔好再去做所謂既快閃RoadBlock<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先快閃RB唔同快閃藍鋪黑鋪<br />\n快閃RB比快閃藍鋪所使用既人力多數倍<br />\n打爛黑藍店可能只需要4人打2人哨<br />\n但快閃rb可能會拉走20人以上<br />\n會分散陣地戰既人力物力<br />\n此外 快閃rb好大機會快閃完比人清<br />\n只係你地快閃完睇唔到<br />\n希望你地將人力集中翻係主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三點<br />\n屯門牛要學習主動尋覓有利戰地<br />\n何謂有利戰地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要分「戰略有利」同「價值有利」<br />\n戰略有利位置<br />\n1. 高位(eg琴日既杯渡輕鐵站)<br />\n2. 有水既地方(屯門河 蔡意橋)<br />\n我地集合地點都一定係要老地方<br />\n集合完再研究下戰地應該建立係邊<br />\n戰地可以繼續vcity十字路<br />\n但請佔領「戰略有利位置」！<br />\n<br />\n價值有利位置<br />\n1. 屯門公路 2. 青山公路<br />\n今日既行動可以選擇轉場去屯公<br />\n因為可以阻止到香港人放工<br />\n聽朝再阻止香港人翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣我地所獲得既行動效益會更大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四點：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\">火魔法師嚴禁冇力人士！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n火魔法燒著哂條布先好Dump！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇完文推文是一種美德！<br />\n睇完文推文都係一種抗爭！<br />\n有改善建議可以下面提出！<br />\n屯門牛 爭氣！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12808a9b04c8e5858c819d2ec87238fbfde303d4","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屯門牛要追上出面既戰績呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"46bacff4d6a91b701e56c731d54e886ad3de38a1","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b822d5768d4ca66927ce903ba0d30f087aaa336","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783ba3281307be78f43c793d3d6b5fe3dc2b422d","tid":1719720,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f753becde74832e4b46ecac00c3c4ff912c997ce","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a76ee902a23ed9e5b379660cdbb3debfe55c15","tid":1719720,"uid":157275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8bb40c706c98c1241106e255f24ea42a31850c4","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d97d3398e4dfeb73a4e870529b3c7519b66c25","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d3d6939a68fc5c8afe953ec42d6c0ff790432e","tid":1719720,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca055c781e6d652de1352c89ee87c9fc60c5b57","tid":1719720,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,